Package: cokpca
Type: Package
Title: Co-Kurtosis Principal Component Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ziheng Wei; Xincheng Zeng; Jialiang Song
Maintainer: Ziheng Wei <zihwei@umich.edu>
Description: Implements Co-Kurtosis Principal Component Analysis (Co-Kurtosis PCA) for dimensionality reduction and data reconstruction. Supports both linear and non-linear (ANN-based) reconstruction methods, with functionality for cumulative contribution analysis, contribution plotting, and loadings visualization.
